an><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/12/02 5:41:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=88.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.succubus.de/smallcross.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: I hate level draining</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> If you dont have access to the spells to reverse/heal it though</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
